{"tid":251813,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北韓下午再試射飛彈 型號尚未公布","createTime":"2017-05-21T09:02:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-21T11:09:18.000Z","uid":35790,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0ee024d0c73fdf98626c28dee98f3968d548e25e","tid":251813,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T09:02:06.000Z","msg":"北韓下午再試射飛彈 型號尚未公布<br />\n<br />\n2017-05-21 16:47<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕北韓又射了！南韓《韓聯社》報導，北韓今天（21日）又傳試射飛彈，目前詳細型號不明，若消息屬實，將是北韓今年第8次試射飛彈。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，北韓今天下午要傳出試射飛彈，不過型號仍未確認，消息由南韓聯合參謀本部報告。<br />\n<br />\n北韓14日才成功試射「火星12型」（Hwasong-12）中長程飛彈，高度達到2111.5公里、飛行距離787公里，飛行約30分鐘後落入日本海。北韓領導人金正恩昨天表示，北韓現時已經成為「東方核強國」及「亞洲火箭霸主」。<br />\n&lt;自由時報&gt;"},{"pid":"25c0e3347bdec04a2afef344a740d471178c2ccc","tid":251813,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T09:02:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c72f523fc88d6a5d90a35c5268bfdfd2b9e14847","tid":251813,"uid":33481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T09:02:46.000Z","msg":"侵侵死左去邊"},{"pid":"1843d34045e9a8c9dbdb11571e112440e9ed28c1","tid":251813,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T09:04:25.000Z","msg":"金仔幾時玩核試？"},{"pid":"97e1063b1ea86e9adcc109eaf70c78270a482056","tid":251813,"uid":7278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T09:06:05.000Z","msg":"會唔會唔小心射左黎香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85e8ade379d7da6645c9fcfd16c15621ac2f4c87","tid":251813,"uid":7278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T09:25:59.000Z","msg":"跌左落海"},{"pid":"142de03902fac2ac29ea60733d665b6d20fe042d","tid":251813,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T09:30:46.000Z","msg":"金仔一向靠沽空軍演獲利<br />\n依排應該輸唔少<br />\n遲早發癲"},{"pid":"31e4f1b141e87448a2f8dd4322e644c20c6a1c29","tid":251813,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s